stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> OrderPlaced: Customer places order
    
    OrderPlaced --> Confirmed: Seller confirms
    Confirmed --> RiderAssigned: Rider accepts
    
    RiderAssigned --> InTransit: Rider picks up order
    RiderAssigned --> CancelledNoRider: No rider available
    
    InTransit --> Delayed: ETA exceeded
    InTransit --> ArrivingSoon: Within 5 min of destination
    
    Delayed --> DelayWarning: System detects delay
    DelayWarning --> DelayOptions: Customer views options
    DelayOptions --> InTransit: Customer waits
    DelayOptions --> CancelledByCustomer: Customer cancels
    DelayOptions --> CompensationApplied: System offers credit
    
    CompensationApplied --> InTransit: Customer accepts
    
    ArrivingSoon --> Delivered: Rider arrives
    InTransit --> Delivered: Rider arrives
    
    Delivered --> QualityVerification: Photos ready
    QualityVerification --> Completed: Customer approves
    QualityVerification --> Rejected: Customer rejects
    
    OrderPlaced --> CancelledByCustomer: Customer cancels
    Confirmed --> CancelledByCustomer: Customer cancels
    RiderAssigned --> CancelledByCustomer: Customer cancels
    
    Confirmed --> CancelledBySeller: Seller cancels
    RiderAssigned --> CancelledBySeller: Seller cancels
    
    CancelledByCustomer --> RefundProcessing: Refund initiated
    CancelledBySeller --> RefundProcessing: Refund initiated
    CancelledNoRider --> RefundProcessing: Refund initiated
    Rejected --> RefundProcessing: Refund initiated
    
    RefundProcessing --> RefundCompleted: Payment processed
    RefundCompleted --> [*]
    Completed --> [*]
    
    note right of Delayed
        Delay Detection:
        - ETA exceeded by 15+ min
        - Rider not moving
        - Traffic detected
    end note
    
    note right of CompensationApplied
        Automatic Compensation:
        - 500 FCFA for 30+ min delay
        - 1000 FCFA for 60+ min delay
    end note
    
    note right of QualityVerification
        KEY DIFFERENTIATOR:
        Customer reviews 3 photos
        taken by rider
    end note

